                                                   "always use fully qualified table names (e.g. <keyspace>.<table>). " +
                                                   "Keyspace used: %s, statement keyspace: %s, statement id: %s", getRawKeyspace(), preparedKeyspace, statementId));
            issuedPreparedStatementsUseWarning = true;
        }
    }

